name: Mashuu Style
description:
LORA trained on the art of Mashuu.

As of rn, for some reason, no one has made a new Mashuu style lora. Despite loras becoming mainstream in this community. So here is mine for anyone who uses loras more than actual embeddings.

300+ images trained on NAI and tested across multiple models. Token not required. NSFW capable.

Images in preview may be from past versions! Do not expect full replication!

Images you make with this model and what you do with them are your responsibility!
